<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<p>
    PodcastApp values your privacy. All user registration and authentication data
    are securely stored in Amazon RDS. Comments data are handled via AWS DynamoDB,
    and no personal information is shared publicly.
</p>
<p>
    By using this application, you agree that:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Your user account is stored in SQL Server (RDS).</li>
    <li>Comments are stored in DynamoDB for scalability.</li>
    <li>Media uploads are stored in S3 for secure access.</li>
</ul>
